---
import Layout from '@/components/chrome/Layout.astro';
import ClusterFunnelBlock from '@/components/chrome/ClusterFunnelBlock.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Contact — strops.tools"
  description="Contact strops.tools. Bug reports, tool requests, partnership inquiries welcome."
  path="/contact"
>
  <article class="bg-parchment">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 pt-12 pb-9 prose">
      <h1 class="text-h1 font-serif text-navy leading-tight">
        Contact<span class="period-accent">.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-lead text-ink-2">
        Found a bug? Have a tool you wish existed? Want to syndicate a calculator? Email is the way.
      </p>

      <h2>Email</h2>
      <p>
        <a href="mailto:hello@strops.tools" class="font-mono">hello@strops.tools</a>
      </p>

      <h2>What works well in an email</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Bug reports</strong> — include the page URL (URL contains your inputs, so we can reproduce immediately), what you expected, what you saw.</li>
        <li><strong>Tool requests</strong> — what's the host problem you're solving? We've got a backlog list and prioritize by host volume.</li>
        <li><strong>Data corrections</strong> — replacement-cost ranges or maintenance cadences out of date? Point us at a verifiable source and we'll update within the week.</li>
        <li><strong>Affiliate inquiries</strong> — smart locks, noise monitors, PMS, cleaner marketplaces — we vet and place by audience fit, not by the highest bid.</li>
        <li><strong>Embed / syndication</strong> — yes, we plan to ship embeddable widget versions; reach out if you want early access.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>What doesn't work</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Tax / legal advice</strong> — STR regulations vary by city and state. We can't answer "is short-term rental legal in city X?" That's a CPA or local-counsel question. We can help you find the source.</li>
        <li><strong>SEO / link partnerships</strong> — we don't do paid backlink swaps.</li>
        <li><strong>Cold sales pitches</strong> — pass.</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        Response time: usually within a week. Faster on bugs and data corrections.
      </p>
    </div>

    <ClusterFunnelBlock currentCluster="operations" />
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose :global(h2) { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--t-h2-size); color: var(--brand-navy); margin-top: var(--sp-7); margin-bottom: var(--sp-3); line-height: 1.1; }
  .prose :global(p) { color: var(--fg-1); margin-bottom: var(--sp-3); line-height: 1.6; }
  .prose :global(ul) { margin: var(--sp-3) 0 var(--sp-4); padding-left: var(--sp-5); }
  .prose :global(li) { margin-bottom: var(--sp-2); line-height: 1.55; }
  .prose :global(strong) { color: var(--brand-navy); font-weight: 600; }
  .prose :global(a) { color: var(--brand-navy); text-decoration: underline; text-decoration-color: var(--brand-gold); text-underline-offset: 3px; }
</style>
